coverLetter: My partner and I moved from Missouri to Oregon to get work with the medicine and potentially trim, we are passionate about medicine and working qith plants, we have completed 3/4 steps of the OLCC permit and passed the certification test. However, we are waiting to have the money to finalize the payment. Hence us looking for work! We are passionate and detail-oriented loyal people, we would love to make a great addition to your team!
